		["moon_and_star"] = "Legendary ring of Indoril Nerevar crafted by the Tonal Architect Lord Kagrenac of the Dwemer and blessed by the Daedric Goddess Azura, this ring provided Nerevar with the means to unite the warring Chimer clans and form the First Council alongside the Dwarves.",
