		-- Yet Another Guard Diversity
		["dnk_ceph_bts"] = "Associated with Great House Telvanni, Cephalopod boots are created by hollowing out and laminating the carapace of the Cephalopod, a sea-dwelling mollusc native to the mainland of Morrowind.",
