		["_rv_hc_boots"] = "Fashioned from laminated insect shell glued with organic resins, Heavy Chitin boots are made even more rigid through the layering of materials and hardening of binding agents with ancient Ashlander techniques, though at the cost of the flexibility usually characteristic of Chitin armor.",
