		["fabricant_machine_1"] = "Trapped soul of a Verminous Fabricant, mysterious creatures engineered by the enigmatic Sotha Sil. Trapped soul of a Verminous Fabricant, mysterious creatures that attacked the Plaza Brindisi Dorom of Mournhold. Despite their similarity to Dwemer Centurions, Fabricants differ in that they are in part organic and contain a soul, possibly derived from the gem that may be powering the creature.",
